### 아카이브 생성
POST http://127.0.0.1:8080/api/v1/archives
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

{
  "emotion": "ANXIOUS",
  "content": "인생의 노잼시기가 왔다..",
  "visibility": "PUBLIC",
  "location": {
    "latitude": 37.566535,
    "longitude": 126.977969,
    "locationLabel": "시청역"
  }
}

### 아카이브 생성
POST http://127.0.0.1:8080/api/v1/archives
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

{
  "emotion": "ANXIOUS",
  "content": "인생의 노잼시기가 왔다..",
  "visibility": "PRIVATE",
  "location": null
}

### [예외] 아카이브 생성
POST http://127.0.0.1:8080/api/v1/archives
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

{
  "emotion": null,
  "content": null,
  "visibility": "PRIVATE",
  "location": null
}

### 아카이브 이미지 등록
POST http://127.0.0.1:8080/api/v1/archives/4/images
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----boundary

------boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="images"; filename="test.png"
Content-Type: image/png

< ./test.png
------boundary

### 아카이브 이미지 삭제
DELETE http://127.0.0.1:8080/api/v1/archives/4/images/6
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### 아카이브 이미지 다운로드
GET http://127.0.0.1:8080/api/v1/archives/1/images/2
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### 아카이브 목록 조회
GET http://127.0.0.1:8080/api/v1/archives?sortType=LATEST&page=0&size=10
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### 아카이브 상세 조회
GET http://127.0.0.1:8080/api/v1/archives/55
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### 나의 아카이브 조회
GET http://127.0.0.1:8080/api/v1/archives/me?sortType=LATEST&page=1&size=10
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### 아카이브 공개/비공개 전환
PATCH http://127.0.0.1:8080/api/v1/archives/55/status
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

{
  "visibility": "PUBLIC"
}
